{"tid":1198510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[sing club]民陣：或起發持續集會，只要人數增加，音響便會升級！","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:56:13.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e49ca1d2afe00ede63ea03b199f115549aef5204","tid":1198510,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"民陣召集人岑子杰指昨日遊行晚上10點完結，11點政府便發出聲明，林鄭月娥明顯是挑釁香港人，測試香港人可以為自己的家「做幾多野，付出幾多，犧牲幾多」，「既憤怒又可悲」。岑子杰稱已有商戶於星期三自發罷工罷課罷市，認為會燃燒下去。<br />\n<br />\n岑子杰表示，只要立法會有相關會議，民陣便會持續發起集會。他不預計集會一開始便會多人，但如人數不斷增加，民陣第二日的音響便會「升級」，「只要有會議，我地就會有行動」，集會會持續至每日的會議結束。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064637&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCPFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=794cbbab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1064637&h=dad8acde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1064637</a>"},{"pid":"b2877109804cc1159caaaefcd1c8d59fcf360a5d","tid":1198510,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d0b6d8fa15b815de99e6bde956360af683f9a1","tid":1198510,"uid":55951,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"升級音響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要你升級抗爭啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65f991c885b3488caa18a1b3b220a909954537f","tid":1198510,"uid":72466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"今天我！"},{"pid":"e8feed7ad16df58a8bd681a0a1aa646b6c9e2f00","tid":1198510,"uid":9542,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"19d0b6d8fa15b815de99e6bde956360af683f9a1","tid":1198510,"uid":55951,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:04:46.00